name: wonderland (itch) (quabmara, Madelaine21)
description:
In this game you are a frog lost in wonderland. You have to find the hole to the next level. But be careful, time is running out! Luckily, you can catch the rabbit who spawns on the map to gain more time. There might be a suprise in the end..

We hope you enjoy playing this little game :)

warning: the game starts right away

controls

w a s d - to move

background music

Music by Aleksey Chistilin Pixabay

https://pixabay.com/music/main-title-alice-in-dark-wonderland-123894/

(because we are bad in music and didn't have any time left)

We made this game in three days for the Mini Jam 126. The theme was 'lost' and the limitation 'time is a resource'.
